msgid "The <guimenu>Physical Extent Size</guimenu> defines the size of a physical block in the volume group. All the disk space in a volume group is handled in chunks of this size. Values can be from 1 KB to 16 GB in powers of 2. This value is normally set to 4&nbsp;MB."
